<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>曾经“感谢贫穷” </span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>如今一身戎装不负韶华</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>加油王心仪！</span></strong><strong><span></span></strong></span></p>
